  "text": "In this section, using the coupled model in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] studies, we present a similar coupled model composed of excitatory and inhibitory neurons with synaptic connections and K ? lateral diffusion. In this model, an excitatory neuron innervates inhibitory neurons via excitatory synapses (AMPA) [CITATION_3] , whereas an inhibitory neuron innervates excitatory neurons via inhibitory synapses (GABAA) [CITATION_4] . The sketch is shown in Fig. 1 .",
